# Local environment and runtime secret files
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.runtime
**/.env.override

# Keep templates tracked
!**/.env.example

# Certificates / private keys (local or generated)
**/*.key
**/*-ca.key
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx

# Build and runtime artifacts
**/dist/
**/build/
**/coverage/
**/*.log
**/tmp/
**/.cache/

# Node modules
**/node_modules/

# Go build artifacts
**/*.exe
**/*.test
**/*.out

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
